## Module Decomposition

```
src/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ index.ts              вҶҗ public API: MapTour.init()
в”ңв”Җв”Җ loader.ts             вҶҗ fetch + parse tour YAML, validate schema
в”ңв”Җв”Җ schema.ts             вҶҗ JSON Schema definition + validation (ajv or manual)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ map/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ MapView.ts        вҶҗ Leaflet map init, pin rendering, route polylines, GPS dot
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ layers.ts         вҶҗ pin icon factory, leg style lookup (walk vs drive)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ card/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ StopCard.ts       вҶҗ stop card DOM controller
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ blocks/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ TextBlock.ts
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ ImageBlock.ts
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ GalleryBlock.ts
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ VideoBlock.ts  вҶҗ YouTube iframe embed
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ AudioBlock.ts
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ NavButton.ts      вҶҗ "Take me there" button, app preference, deep-link
в”ңв”Җв”Җ navigation/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ NavController.ts  вҶҗ Prev/Next, active stop state, map re-centre
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ NavAppPreference.ts вҶҗ localStorage-backed app choice (Maps/Waze/Google)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ breadcrumb/
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ Breadcrumb.ts     вҶҗ visited set in localStorage, pin decoration
в”ңв”Җв”Җ gps/
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ GpsTracker.ts     вҶҗ Geolocation API wrapper, broadcasts position events
в””в”Җв”Җ errors/
    в””в”Җв”Җ ErrorDisplay.ts   вҶҗ renders human-readable errors into the container div
```

---

## Tour YAML Data Model

```yaml
# tour.yaml
tour:
  id: ett-2025
  title: Enniscorthy Tidy Towns 2025
  description: A guided tour of this year's projects.

stops:
  - id: 1
    title: Town Square Planting
    coords: [52.5022, -6.5581]
    content:
      - type: text
        body: "Markdown paragraph..."
      - type: image
        url: https://drive.google.com/.../photo.jpg
        caption: Before and after
      - type: gallery
        images:
          - url: https://...
            caption: Caption
      - type: video
        url: https://youtube.com/watch?v=...
      - type: audio
        url: https://...
        label: Commentary by John Smith
    leg_to_next:
      mode: walk          # walk | drive
      note: "Follow river path, ~8 min"

  - id: 2
    title: River Cleanup Site
    coords: [52.5041, -6.5563]
    content:
      - type: text
        body: "..."
```

**Validation rules:**
- `tour.id`, `tour.title` required
- Each stop requires `id` (unique integer), `title`, `coords` (2-element array of numbers)
- `content` array may be empty but must be present
- `type` in each block must be one of: `text`, `image`, `gallery`, `video`, `audio`
- `leg_to_next.mode` must be `walk` or `drive`
- Unknown keys are warned, not errored

---

## Integration Contract (Public API)

```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="maptour.css">
<div id="maptour"></div>
<script src="maptour.js"></script>
<script>
  MapTour.init({
    container: '#maptour',   // CSS selector or Element
    tourUrl: './tour.yaml',  // relative or absolute URL
    // optional:
    startStop: 1,            // open on this stop id
  });
</script>
```

**CSS custom properties (with defaults):**
```css
:root {
  --maptour-primary: #2563eb;
  --maptour-surface: #ffffff;
  --maptour-text: #111827;
  --maptour-accent: #16a34a;
  --maptour-font: system-ui, sans-serif;
  --maptour-radius: 8px;
}
```

---

## Non-Functional Architecture

| Concern | Approach |
|---|---|
| GPS unavailable | GpsTracker broadcasts null; MapView renders no dot; no crash |
| Media URL fails | Each block has an `onError` handler; shows placeholder text |
| YAML parse error | ErrorDisplay renders message into container div |
| localStorage unavailable | Breadcrumb + NavAppPreference degrade to in-memory only |
| Leaflet tile server down | Tiles blank; pins/polylines still visible (Leaflet behaviour) |
| Large tour | Pins rendered in one batch on load; no lazy loading needed at вүӨ100 stops |

---

