---

## Tech Stack Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Language | TypeScript | Type safety for data model parsing; compiles to plain JS |
| Build | Vite | Produces IIFE bundle natively; fast; no config ceremony |
| Map | Leaflet | OSM-based, no API key, MIT licence, small footprint |
| YAML parser | `js-yaml` | Battle-tested, MIT, handles YAML 1.2 |
| Unit tests | Vitest | Native TS, fast, compatible with Vite setup |
| E2E tests | Playwright | Cross-browser, headless, works against a local static server |
| CSS | Plain CSS with custom properties | No build dependency for theming; integrators override vars |

---

## Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Google Drive link expiry or access change | Medium | High | Document this limitation clearly; recommend public share links |
| YouTube iframe blocked by host CSP | Low | Medium | Document CSP requirement in integration guide |
| Geolocation permission denied on iOS Safari | Medium | Low | GPS is enhancement only; graceful degradation |
| Bundle size creep beyond 200 KB | Low | Medium | Track with CI size budget check |
| Tour author publishes invalid YAML | High | Medium | Clear error display + JSON Schema + example file |
